OL,5, KFC Nigeria has issued an apology after
OL,6, the country's airport authority shut   
OL,7, one of its outlets over the alleged    
OL,8, discrimination of a disabled client.   
OL,10,FAdebola Daniel, son of a former        
OL,11,FNigerian state governor Gbenga Daniel, 
OL,12,Fsaid in a post on X that he was ordered
OL,13,Fto leave a KFC outlet at Lagos airport 
OL,14,Fbecause of his wheelchair.             
OL,16,FThe post sparked widespread outrage.   
OL,18,FIt also prompted an investigation by   
OL,19,Fthe federal airport authority, ending  
OL,20,Fin the branch's closure.               
